      "note": "Summary of Original Version",
      "abstract": "Amend KRS 456.010 to define \"school violence\"; amend KRS 456.030 to allow a victim of school violence to file a petition for an interpersonal protective order; amend various sections of KRS Chapter 456 to conform."
